47
00:03:28,416 --> 00:03:30,499
To me she was Norma Jean.

48
00:03:32,354 --> 00:03:34,981
Always was, always will be.

49
00:03:34,981 --> 00:03:37,481
(upbeat jazz)

50
00:03:43,228 --> 00:03:45,165
I was writing stories about movie stars

51
00:03:45,165 --> 00:03:47,412
