but I didn't want to leave.

56
00:03:56,697 --> 00:03:58,531
And then, one morning while I was waiting

57
00:03:58,531 --> 00:04:01,198
to interview a casting director.

58
00:04:15,674 --> 00:04:16,507
You okay?

59
00:04:20,815 --> 00:04:23,859
- And then the very moment,
the danger was over.

60
00:04:23,859 --> 00:04:25,588
It was as if nothing had happened.

61
00:04:25,588 --> 00:04:28,338
I was again your doll, your lark.

62
00:04:29,611 --> 00:04:30,444
- Excuse me?

63
00:04:30,444 --> 00:04:33,795
- It's from the play you
were reading, A Doll's House.

64
00:04:33,795 --> 00:04:34,956
I did Nora in Van Nuys.

65
00:04:34,956 --> 00:04:35,875
- Oh, I see.

66
