73
00:04:49,444 --> 00:04:50,442
- I'm Norma Jean Baker.

74
00:04:50,442 --> 00:04:52,109
- [Bob] Bob Slatzer.

75
00:04:53,331 --> 00:04:54,966
- I think I'll call you Ibsen.

76
