find a place of your own.

234
00:14:06,824 --> 00:14:08,657
If you need any money,

235
00:14:12,017 --> 00:14:15,517
you know I love you, like you were my own.

236
00:14:16,929 --> 00:14:18,518
- I know, Aunt Dana.

237
00:14:18,518 --> 00:14:20,576
Everyone loves me.

238
00:14:20,576 --> 00:14:23,743
Sooner or later everyone says goodbye.

239
00:14:35,492 --> 00:14:37,742
(knocking)

240
00:14:48,050 --> 00:14:50,923
